706811f-a.text:
Smith Sreet, east side, north from 3rd to 2nd Streets, as seen from
Second Place.
June 5, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.

706812f-b.text:
(1)
Smith Street, north from 3rd Street, at the right. At the left, work is in progress on the new Eighth Ave., Subway.
October 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Cellection.
(2)
The same, showing Smith Street, four years later, after the subway was constructed. It the foreground, right, is Second Street.
June S, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
